#Risk Assessment Summary
The FinSecure infrastructure contains several security weaknesses related to outdated protocols, insufficient encryption, network configuration issues, and limited monitoring capabilities.
Addressing these vulnerabilities through stronger encryption standards, improved access controls, secure network configurations, and centralized monitoring would significantly improve the
organization’s security posture and reduce the risk of data compromise.
